        <num>CCP 4392</num>
        <heading>4392.  Final account</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 4392.  Final account
A tutor may file a final account at any time after expiration of the tutorship.
The court shall order the filing of a final account upon the application of the former minor after the expiration of the tutorship, or upon the rendition of a judgment ordering the removal of a tutor or authorizing his resignation.</p>
        </content>
